{"tid":1949170,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【抵制TVB週日任】藍絲也抵制，將雪印醜聞傳俾藍絲！ (29 Mar)","createTime":"2020-03-29T12:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T06:38:33.000Z","uid":267969,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"82bca4612ac1ce14122c6cce373aebfed4df273d","tid":1949170,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />週日特別任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />29 Mar 2020】</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBhHGC8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBhHGC8.jpg&h=6a585233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚔️【行動概要】<br />\n仲喺TVB落廣告嘅品牌，一定唔care香港人嘅感愛，或者藍底紅底🔹🇨🇳<br />\n藍絲最驚係乜？驚死囉☠️～所以我哋要做下好心，將品牌真實嘅產品問題spread俾藍絲，等佢哋都加入抵制大軍🤪<br />\n<br />\n⚔️【行動詳情】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Step 1️⃣ 去Discuss, Uwants, Babycondom推post</span></strong><br />\n⚠️注意事項：<br />\n💢俾少少心機回覆，如果只係回覆&quot;推&quot;、表情灌水，嚴重者可能被封鎖帳戶<br />\n💢Template：&quot;真係好恐怖&quot;, &quot;日本牌子都唔係安全&quot;<br />\n💢隔幾日再回覆，推足一星期<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻Discuss<br />\n<a href=\"https://ladies.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28959731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fladies.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D28959731&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=28a42e85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ladies.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28959731</a><br />\n👉🏻Uwants<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=20124906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D20124906&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=55743094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=20124906</a><br />\n👉🏻親子王國<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=23147877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.baby-kingdom.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D23147877&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=a7fe9365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.baby-kingdom.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=23147877</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Step 2️⃣ Whatsapp</span></strong><br />\n將雪印醜聞傳spread去Whatsapp長者group、媽媽group，請喺留言搵圖及文字<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Step 3️⃣ 進階 - 開post：</span></strong><br />\n喺唔同討論區相關分台自行開post，但如果見到手足已開post，推post就得（請注意相關版規）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. Discuss嗰班TVB柒fans好期待我哋入去影視台踩場，我哋偏偏唔入去，歡迎佢哋幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e672a69c01b36d28ef978e960458ea1660ed64b","tid":1949170,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afecfb91b868ad742a75033b68c3eea5620167ee","tid":1949170,"uid":267969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Whatsapp Template 短版</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYioq5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYioq5x.jpg&h=d88e0e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 😱😱😱<br />\n真係好恐怖，雪印呢間日本公司成日出產品問題<br />\n2000年, 2002年, 2012年, 2017年都有<br />\n小日本唔係樣樣都信得過😣<br />\n【二千多支牛乳未經註冊要回收】<br />\n2017年5月22日<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2wVZsW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wVZsW4&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=0fb5a6e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2wVZsW4</a><br />\n【東方報道「雪印」驚現奶粉蟲】<br />\n2012年10月27日<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UN6CEr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UN6CEr&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=d8879b1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UN6CEr</a><br />\n【雪印過期牛油製奶】<br />\n2002年2月24日<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39TvrET\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39TvrET&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b3ccb4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39TvrET</a><br />\n【循環再用過期奶製品，萬人中毒】<br />\n2000年6月及2002年<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aZSQVg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aZSQVg&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=fed30956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aZSQVg</a>"},{"pid":"d8bbe5728f2dd013f331862cad82ae57b1b9f969","tid":1949170,"uid":201678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d902c5fc302cfcbe528b4131c8fc92b41b48328","tid":1949170,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"連登影視台嗰班tvb狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76853b8debb18e545b13f76ec11eab95a86207a8","tid":1949170,"uid":267969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Whatsapp Template 長版</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYioq5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYioq5x.jpg&h=d88e0e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 😱😱😱<br />\n真係好恐怖，雪印呢間日本公司成日出產品問題<br />\n2000年, 2002年, 2012年, 2017年都有<br />\n小日本唔係樣樣都信得過😣<br />\n<br />\n【二千多支牛乳未經註冊要回收】<br />\n2017年5月22日<br />\n//食物安全中心發現雪印兩款北海道牛乳，未經批准入口，呼籲市民不要飲用，要求業界停售、下架及回收。涉及的牛奶由味之誘惑公司進口，其中一公升裝的食用日期是下月二十四日之前，二百毫升裝是下月二十三日之前。<br />\n食安中心指，進口商入口兩款盒裝牛奶一千二百多盒，部分分發到旗下零售點出售，已指令回收//<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2wVZsW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wVZsW4&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=0fb5a6e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2wVZsW4</a><br />\n<br />\n【東方報道「雪印」驚現奶粉蟲】<br />\n2012年10月27日<br />\n//雪印奶粉驚現疑似毛髮及蟲屍，嚇壞好爸爸。居於鴨脷洲的男事主，日前在區內連鎖藥房，購買雪印「思敏兒1」初生嬰兒奶粉，給女兒食用，惟先後在兩罐奶粉中發現毛髮及蟲屍物體，他感十分驚嚇，更擔心愛女健康受影響，食環署接獲事主投訴，檢走奶粉及可疑物體檢驗。雪印香港有限公司表示，生產過程不經人手，奶粉罐密封，相信不可能生蟲。公司會全力協助食環署調查//<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UN6CEr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UN6CEr&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=d8879b1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UN6CEr</a><br />\n<br />\n【雪印過期牛油製奶】<br />\n2002年2月24日<br />\n//周末又被揭發改寫雪藏牛油的保鮮日期，並用七百六十噸過期牛油來製造牛奶及雪糕。雖然此舉不一定違法，卻是繼牛肉標籤醜聞後，對該公司另一次打擊。<br />\n共同社上周六報道，雪印今年一月將北海道一間廠房的二千三百噸已過期的雪藏牛油，重新包裝運到各雪印工廠，其中七百六十噸被製成牛奶和雪糕//<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39TvrET\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39TvrET&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b3ccb4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39TvrET</a><br />\n<br />\n【循環再用過期奶製品，萬人中毒】<br />\n2000年6月及2002年<br />\n//雪印乳品食物中毒事件發生在2000年6月期間，起因於雪印生產乳製品的工廠曾在同年3月發生停電，使生乳暴露在常溫超過4小時，但雪印公司居然繼續將這批受毒素汙染的生乳加工販售，造成關西地區將近1萬5千人食物中毒，是日本國內自從戰後規模最大的食物中毒事件。<br />\n2002年日本國內碰上狂牛症疫情，政府要求農協收購國產牛肉清查、銷毀，並由政府補助相關費用，沒想到雪印食品公司擅自將澳洲進口牛肉更改包裝、假造製造日期，偽裝成日本本土牛肉以「冒領政府補助」//<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aZSQVg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aZSQVg&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=fed30956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aZSQVg</a>"},{"pid":"e8c8cf9ec4c8195b933f31a8d70da2012735ca95","tid":1949170,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b3263c37148d069c9861647cda9cbdedbd3f7f2","tid":1949170,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T12:57:47.0